ks and interference sources to improve your connection quality.\n- **AR-Powered Visualization:** Utilize mixed reality to see your network\u2019s performance through your Meta Quest headset.\n\nWhether you\u2019re a network enthusiast, a professional, or someone just looking to improve their WiFi, WiVi offers the tools you need to optimize your wireless experience.", "short_description": "Explore and map your WiFi like never before with WiVi, the AR-powered tool that visualizes your signal strength, internet speed, and interference in the world around you.\n\nWalk through your home or office to build a detailed map of the space. Ideal for optimizing your wireless setup for streaming games or video meetings."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.niftysoftar.com/wivi-privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.niftysoftar.com/wivi-terms-of-service", "publisher_name": "Niftysoft Technologies LLC", "support_website_url": "https://www.niftysoftar.com/feedback", "website_url": "https://www.niftysoftar.com/", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1063584910766706"}, {"id": "421923165850360"}, {"id": "393222478507326"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "8156458974469115"}}]}, "scheduled_offers": {"count": 1, "nodes": [{"status": "PUBLISHED", "id": "1089134113214789"}]}, "baseline_offer": {"id": "1089134113214789"}, "is_approved": true, "firstOffer": {"nodes": [{"start_ti